name: Rocket Rampage (Cinnamatsu)
description:
Welcome to ROCKET RAMPAGE!

The Alienoids have gone too far this time. They're taking over the universe (with their astoundingly cute looks)!

It's time for this little rocket to go on a big rampage filled with bullets, explosions, alien UFOs, and a lot of cheesy one-liners!

CREDITS:

BGM "Fantastic Voyage" by SergeQuadrado - https://freesound.org/people/SergeQuadrado/sounds/670093/

All other sound effects created from my mouth.

All sprites, artwork and animation created by me!
